('d8d94b18-599b-4f1e-a708-a6ee7db7818f', 'Introduction to Information Security', 'Information security, also known as cybersecurity or IT security, is the practice of protecting computer systems, networks, and sensitive information from unauthorized access, use, disclosure, disruption, modification, or destruction. It involves using various measures and technologies to safeguard digital assets and prevent them from being compromised, stolen, or lost.', '2023-04-03 02:30:03', '2023-04-03 02:30:03', 'acd6f5ae-5c57-47aa-996d-5a877f9bf0fb'),
